Simone, I have some questions for you:<br>
<br>
Why would a SINGLE woman who MUST return to work to support herself and her baby <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>choose</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> to have children in the first place? Would you prefer she abort? Or should she remain celebate rather than risk pregnancy, birth and the dreaded daycare?<br>
