<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>I have no doubt that this arrangement is better for her than if I stayed home with her full-time--can you understand why I feel that way in this situation?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->[/quote]<br>
